ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[Extension plant pathologists in several states have been contacted to
determine whether there are other outbreaks. The disease has not been
reported on tomato in Arizona, New Jersey, New York (last report was in
1993), or Oregon. It has been reported in Kentucky (lowest incidence in 5
years) and on tobacco, but not on tomato, in Maryland. - Mod.DH]
